						<div class="postbody">Assemblers only assemble code, it doesn't know what a screen is or anything, so no it doesn't handle anything with the system. But also isn't something to worry about so much, just don't put anything important in the left+right 8 pixels, and top and bottom 16 pixels on the maps or UI or whatnot.</div>

